1. create a listview in main xml file
2. Create a design file as per your requirement
3. Create a model class as per the design file
4. viewbinding of data in main kt file
5. decalre mutablelist and initialize mutablelist
6. set data in model through set
7. create an adpater file 
	1->return list size
	2->return position
	3->return position in long
	4->inflate view[design file] [get data through model or list]
8.call adapter in main kt file and display data in listview
